"674","Item 61"
"675","Additional Information About Minimum Required Investment"
"676","Shareholders can open a fund account with as little as $500 and"
"677","make subsequent investments in any amount. The minimum investment"
"678","is waived if you make regular investments weekly, semi-monthly,"
"679","or monthly through automatic deductions through your bank"
"680","checking or savings account. Currently, Putnam is waiving the"
"681","minimum, but reserves the right to reject initial investments"
"682","under the minimum."
